# Runtime secrets injected into the platform-runtime container.
#
# Issue #762: shared GDC_WINDOWS_ADMIN_PASSWORD / GDC_KALI_PASSWORD /
# GDC_UBUNTU_PASSWORD entries were removed. Guest passwords are now
# per-instance GCP Secret Manager secrets created at provisioning time
# by shifter/engine/provisioner/gdc_vmruntime_assets.py
# (_ensure_rdp_password_secret) and resolved by the portal through
# shared.cloud at RDP access time.
#
# Add new entries below only when they cannot be sourced from a per-
# range / per-instance secret reference.
